Who are the users?
The users of this app are real estate investors who want to an easy way to keep track of their investments.

What can the users do?
The users will be able to upload their receipts and important documents, keep track of their expenses and income, link receipts to them, and visualize the data.

How can the users do it?
The users can do it by logging into the website, creating a new property, adding expenses and receipts, and then linking the receipts. Each property will have tabs for all of these activities.


What is the user experience going to be like?
It is going to be very simple and streamlined. The user will be able to navigate to the functions that they need by clicking on a property that they have.